# Multi-Domain Language Redirects
# Turkish URLs should be on yapayzekapratik.com
https://ki-automatisieren.de/tr/* https://yapayzekapratik.com/tr/:splat 301!
https://ki-automatisieren.de/tr https://yapayzekapratik.com/tr 301!

# German URLs should be on ki-automatisieren.de  
https://yapayzekapratik.com/de/* https://ki-automatisieren.de/de/:splat 301!
https://yapayzekapratik.com/de https://ki-automatisieren.de/de 301!

# Root redirects to default language
https://ki-automatisieren.de/ https://ki-automatisieren.de/de 302
https://yapayzekapratik.com/ https://yapayzekapratik.com/tr 302

# Sitemap & Robots
/sitemap.xml /functions/v1/sitemap 301
/robots.txt /robots.txt 200
